    · exact .prime 3 1 _ (by pratt) (by reduce_mod_char; decide) (by norm_num)
    · exact .prime 311 1 _ (by pratt) (by reduce_mod_char; decide) (by norm_num)
    · exact .prime 5521 1 _ (by pratt) (by reduce_mod_char; decide) (by norm_num)
    · exact .prime 19861 1 _ (by pratt) (by reduce_mod_char; decide) (by norm_num)
